headline: Does Cisco Stock Still Offer Value After 33% Gain and Digital Infrastructure Push?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Cisco Systems stock? You are definitely not alone. With shares closing most recently at $67.75 and putting up an impressive 33.4% gain over the past year, Cisco continues to turn heads. Investors have seen the stock climb more than 100% in the last five years, defying skeptics and rewarding anyone riding the wave. In just the past week, Cisco inched up another 1.1%, which, while not a dramatic leap, signals resilience in a market that seems to be weighing both...
